<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline-width: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">为促进我校毕业生更加充分更高质量就业，5月16日，江西省2024届高校毕业生春季百校联动校园招聘系列活动暨江西软件职业技术大学2024年春季双选会在我校隆重举行。校党委书记、督导专员江延湖等校领导出席活动，招就处处长、各学院书记等陪同参加活动。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="outline-width: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiie