visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><span style="text-align: justify; visibility: visible; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline-width: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">据统计，本次双选会现场共收到简历</span><span style="text-align: justify; visibility: visible; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline-width: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">700余份，初步达成意向227人，为我校2024届毕业生提供了大量的就业机会。下一步，我校还将通过线上、线下多种渠道为毕业生们提供更加全面优质的就业指导服务，促进我校毕业生充分就业。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>